// playbook contains instructions needed to setup your virtual machine eg install apache in this example

command: ansible-galaxy init role_name -> create roles that perform certain actions


add vagrant box
 - vagrant box add ubuntu/jammy64

 start up vagrant
  - vagrant up

ssh into vagrant
- vagrant ssh

kill the virtual box running
- vagrant halt

update the virtual box image using vagrant (it will run from the ansible playbook)
- vagrant provision

